review_blob: A dark beer with a heavy impression, in fact, it is not heavy at all.  It has a light taste with a dry follow thru.  The first Sam Smith that I havent been to impressed with.
Not as good as the Sweetwater IPA but good.  Nice floral with good hops and a slight bitterness at the end.  Again, I havent found a Sam Smith that I didnt like yet.
Large hops with a fantastic aroma.  All good natural flavors and again one of my favorite.
Nice aroma with a crisp follow thru.  I havent found a Sam Smith that didnt like yet.
beer_name: Samuel Smiths Pure Brewed Organic Lager

review_blob: An excellent, nice dark beer and not as heavy and the color indicates.  Smooth finish and not at all filling. One of my favorite.
